# Godot 4 web exports use SharedArrayBuffer (threads), which browsers only
# allow when the page is "cross-origin isolated". These two headers turn that
# on. Netlify and Cloudflare Pages both read this _headers file; it must sit
# in the root of the deployed folder (next to index.html).
/*
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
  Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: require-corp
